<D>__{i will be locking you in. no one knows you're here. so keep as quiet as possible.}
<A>__{he nods and goes. the sound of the padlock closing. szpilman takes in the room. he sees the piano, is still for a moment, then goes to it. he sits on the piano stool and adjusts its height. he opens the lid. a cloth covers the keys. he removes the cloth. he gazes lovingly at the keyboard. he flexes his fingers. then, without touching the keys, his fingers floating just above them, he plays. silently. passionately.}
